social_posts.post_text: Some snaps from this past week filled with family, good food and love. I hope everyone had a wonderful holiday.

#Ad I’m always down for a fun adventure. Thank you @Lincoln for inviting me to celebrate your 100th anniversary and for choosing me to be part of #lincoln100 faces. I’m so impressed with Lincoln’s elegant design and futuristic features. I’m looking forward to taking one out on the road!! 

2022 Lincoln Nautilus Reserve model shown with available features.
2022 Lincoln Navigator shown with available features.
Christmas tree is staying up until we open all the Christmas presents. Rumor has it Santa isn’t done shopping yet. When do you take down holiday decor? @themuskodaylakehouse
Can’t believe we’re only 2hrs north of NYC, this feels like we’re so far away. #catskills#snowday#catskillmountains#ilovenyc#upstateny#lakehouse#cozyhouse#snowedin#march2023#airbnb#roscoe#visitroscoe

The fact that I get to experience living in this amazing city, walking it’s streets, and flying it’s skies is beyond amazing to me. I still have to pinch myself every time I’m up here🚁 so see if it’s really real. Thank you @flynyon for flying me since 2013. 😅❤️
Took the hot dogs out for a swim @themuskodaylakehouse
A time of uncertainty is a time of possibility ❤️

Happy Father’s Day @rmanganaro !! You are the absolutely best daddy to our little Leo. Thank you for being the proudest, funnest, most loving and supportive daddy I could have ever dreamed of! Thank you for everything that you do for us every single day! ❤️
Still the best pumpkin patch ever! Happy Halloween 🎃
